Job Posting App

Database:
https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/arshkon/linkedin-job-postings

Features:
Connected Express app to MongoDB using Mongoose.
Created JobPosting schema and model.
Implemented full CRUD routes (GET, POST, PUT, DELETE).
Added validation middleware for job data.
Enhanced GET route with searching, sorting, and pagination features.
Tested and working on Postman.
